-- Jose Mourinho to Sign $16 Million Annual Deal at Real, Sun Says
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2012-05-05T14:43:32Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-05/jose-mourinho-to-sign-16-million-annual-deal-at-real-sun-says.html
Real Madrid coach  Jose Mourinho  will
sign a new contract paying him 10 million pounds ($16 million)
per year after taxes, the Sun said.  Mourinho has been offered a three-year contract worth
190,000 pounds per week to stay at Real until 2015 and is
expected to sign any day soon, the Sun said.  Mourinho, who led Real to its 32nd Spanish league title
this week, has been linked with a move back to former club
Chelsea.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  